OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FA woman has described 'horrific'
OL,7,Fconditions in A&E claiming her 80-year-
OL,8,Fold father was forced to wait 40 hours
OL,9,Fin a corridor for a hospital bed at
OL,10,FArrowe Park on the Wirral.
OL,12,FColin Gray's daughter Kirsty rushed
OL,13,F250 miles from her home in Hampshire
OL,14,Fwhen he was taken to the hospital
OL,15,Fafter becoming ill on 30 December.
OL,17,FColin had a pacemaker fitted to his
OL,18,Fheart last November and was admitted
OL,19,Fto Arrowe Park after becoming unwell
OL,20,Fwith shortness of breath and fatigue.
