OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FWhen she arrived at the hospital to be
OL,7,Fwith her dad Kirsty was horrified by
OL,8,Fwhat she saw.
OL,10,FShe said: "It was horrific in that A&E
OL,11,Fdepartment, it was absolutely rammed.
OL,12,FThere were 15 ambulances queuing up
OL,13,Foutside and lots of paramedics who
OL,14,Fcouldn't hand their patients over.
OL,15,FThere were long queues of people in
OL,16,Fbeds in the corridor."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
