OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FKirsty adds, "Mum stayed with dad all
OL,7,Fnight while he was in a bed on a
OL,8,Fpacked corridor. She said the staff
OL,9,Fwere amazing and looked after them as
OL,10,Fwell as they could, but he was there
OL,11,Ffor over 40 hours in total. This was
OL,12,Fan 80-year-old man, basically shoved
OL,13,Fagainst a wall in a corridor who was
OL,14,Fvery poorly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
