OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,F"He didn't even have any monitoring
OL,7,Fequipment on him, he was just there on
OL,8,Fa bed. They just didn't have enough
OL,9,Fstaff there and those who were there
OL,10,Fwere doing their best but were on
OL,11,Ftheir knees. I can't tell you how
OL,12,Flovely they were despite working in
OL,13,Fextremely challenging circumstances."
OL,15,FColin was eventually moved from the
OL,16,Fcorridor to the Acute Medical Unit,
OL,17,Fbut Ms Gray said this was 'essentially
OL,18,Fjust an overflow for A&E'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
