OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FHaving first arrived at the hospital
OL,7,Fat around 3pm on December 30, he did
OL,8,Fnot see a consultant doctor until 9pm
OL,9,Fon January 2. His full treatment would
OL,10,Fnot begin for around a week in total.
OL,12,FA second critical incident at Arrowe
OL,13,FPark Hospital was declared this week,
OL,14,Fand though Kirsty and her dad are full
OL,15,Fof praise for the work of the staff
OL,16,Fwho cared for him, they say their
OL,17,Fexperiences make them fear for the
OL,18,Ffuture of the nation's health service.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
