OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FKirsty said: "Dad was in was in
OL,7,Fhospital for a week before any proper
OL,8,Ftreatment was done. He was exhausted
OL,9,Fand angry at the state of the NHS. He
OL,10,Fwas really upset to see the staff
OL,11,Fmembers working in these
OL,12,Fcircumstances."
OL,14,FKirsty said she has made complaints to
OL,15,Fthe Wirral University Teaching
OL,16,FHospital Trust and its chief executive
OL,17,FJanelle Holmes, asking for a meeting
OL,18,Fabout how the trust is dealing with
OL,19,Fthe current situation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
