OL,3,C'Horrific' scenes in A and E - 80 year
OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FLike many hospitals in the Merseyside
OL,7,Fregion, Arrowe Park is under huge
OL,8,Fpressure at present with soaring flu
OL,9,Fcases. The trust that runs the
OL,10,Fhospital was forced to declare a
OL,11,Fcritical incident last weekend as it
OL,12,Fstruggled to safely deliver care amid
OL,13,Fthe huge demand.
OL,15,FHaving stood that incident down, the
OL,16,Ftrust declared a second critical
OL,17,Fincident on Wednesday due to what it
OL,18,Fsaid was 'unprecedented demand'.
OL,19,FEarlier in the week, the Royal
OL,20,FLiverpool Hospital also declared a
OL,21,Fcritical incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
