OL,4,Cold man's 40 hour wait in corridor
OL,6,FIn a statement a Wirral University
OL,7,FTeaching Hospital spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"As with other trusts, our Emergency
OL,9,FDepartment has experienced
OL,10,Funprecedented demand with high numbers
OL,11,Fof patients self-presenting and
OL,12,Farriving by ambulance. We prioritise
OL,13,Fpatients in most urgent need of
OL,14,Femergency care and unfortunately this
OL,15,Fwill have meant a longer than expected
OL,16,Fwait for other patients, especially
OL,17,Fthose awaiting hospital admission.
OL,18,FThere have been many patients
OL,19,Frequiring admission to hospital,
OL,20,Fincluding a high number of flu cases.
