OL,6,F"We regret that this has been a
OL,7,Fdifficult experience for the patient,
OL,8,Fand our senior team has been in
OL,9,Fcontact with the patient and his
OL,10,Ffamily throughout to ensure they are
OL,11,Ffully supported, and our PALS team are
OL,12,Ffollowing up with a formal response to
OL,13,Fthe family's concerns.
