OL,6,F"To increase capacity, we have been
OL,7,Fworking closely with our partners to
OL,8,Fdischarge patients home or back into
OL,9,Fthe community, as soon as they no
OL,10,Flonger require a hospital stay. Our
OL,11,FEmergency Department remains busy at
OL,12,Fthis time and we would ask the public
OL,13,Ffor support.
