OL,6,F"People are asked to please only
OL,7,Fattend the Emergency Department if
OL,8,Fthey have a genuine emergency. For
OL,9,Fless urgent needs, people can contact
OL,10,F111, visit a walk-in centre, urgent
OL,11,Ftreatment centre or contact a GP.
OL,12,FPharmacies can also offer assistance
OL,13,Ffor many minor illnesses."
